Judith Richards Hope, a senior partner with the law firm of Paul, Hastings, Janofsky & Walker of Los Angeles, was elected a director of this consumer foods company.
She succeeds retiring directors Gwendolyn A. Newkirk, a University of Nebraska professor, and Edward S. Reid, a partner with the New York law firm of Davis, Polk & Wardwell.
The company now has 16 directors. 

